data.description: Welcome to the prestigious gated community of Bella Charca! This stunning corner lot property boasts an impressive curb appeal with its three-car side entry garage and expansive grounds. As you step through the arched entry, you'll be greeted by an elegant formal dining area adorned with crown molding, setting the tone for luxurious living. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring gorgeous granite countertops, double ovens, a gas cooktop, and stainless steel appliances. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or enjoying a quiet family meal, this kitchen is sure to impress. The primary suite offers a tranquil retreat with a soaking tub, large shower, and a makeup vanity. The spacious walk-in closet provides ample storage for your wardrobe and accessories. Additionally, the home includes a conveniently located laundry room complete with a sink and cabinets, making chores a breeze. Outside, the large patio beckons you to relax and entertain in style. Imagine hosting summer barbecues with friends and family in your very own outdoor oasis. The built-in kitchen ensures that you have everything you need for outdoor culinary delights. Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional property in the sought-after Bella Charca community. Schedule your private viewing today and experience the epitome of comfortable and stylish living.
